discourse_list.title: Moving 30th Nov and 7th Dec Executives to Friday of each week

content.content: Moving 30th Nov & 7th Dec Executives to Friday for each respective week Hi all, A quick notice to inform you that based on the size of the spell content, and the additional writing and reviewing work for the following two executives, PECU and StarkNet teams are moving the mainnet deployments:  From Wednesday the 30th of November to Friday the 2nd of December, and From Wednesday the 7th of December to Friday the 9th of December.  Therefore, both executives for the current and following week will take place on Friday instead of Wednesday for their respective weeks in order to give us enough time to safely deploy Maker community requests as these will be the final executive votes for 2022.
This topic was automatically closed 30 days after the last reply. New replies are no longer allowed.
